    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Opening this vial unleashes its destructive contents: a reconstituted Gargantuan cave worm. The worm has two functions; choose which one to use when you Activate the item. \n* **Burrow** The worm Burrows up to 80 feet, leaving a tunnel behind it. It can burrow through solid stone, but if it does so it burrows 40 feet instead of 80 feet.\n* **Eat** The worm attempts to swallow a creature, crush it in its insides, then spit the creature out. The target must be within 15 feet, and it attempts a DC 30 Reflex save. If it fails, it takes 3d6+9 bludgeoning damage (doubled on a critical failure). The worm then spits the creature out to any empty space on the ground within 30 feet, causing the creature to take damage from a 20-foot fall.",
        "level": 13,
        "traits": [
            {
